Compilation flags:
========================================
Enable : MODEL=HYDRO, GRAVITY, GREP, EOS=EOS_NUCLEAR
Disable: UNSPLIT_GRAVITY

Default setup:
========================================
1. Enable external potential
   --> OPT__EXT_POT = 3

Note:
========================================
1. A test problem for core-collapse supernova simulations
   --> initial condition is generated from FLASH, 15 ms after core bounce

      data_s20GREP_SFHo_15ms           : SFHo  EoS
      data_s20GREP_LS220_nonupres_15ms : LS220 EoS, w/o neutrino
      data_s20GREP_LS220_15ms_none     : LS220 EoS, w/o neutrino and lightbulb
      data_s20GREP_LS220_15ms_LB3      : LS220 EoS, w/o neutrino, with lightbulb (lnu = 1.2e52, tnu = 4 MeV)
      data_s20GREP_LS220_15ms_idsa     : LS220 EoS, with IDSA

2. Each column represents

      radius, mass, dens, ye, velr, temp, pres, entr, ynu1, ynu2, znu1, znu2

   at different radii
